  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/8d5ea2670784efe185ae9859e770d53b.avif?t=1737707855\" width=616 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/dae07bbc9479124ba627a25c735f782d.poster.avif?t=1737707855\" width=716 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/dae07bbc9479124ba627a25c735f782d.webm?t=1737707855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/dae07bbc9479124ba627a25c735f782d.mp4?t=1737707855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon 8 heroes to accompany you, each with unique skills, to face the surging tide of enemies and experience the joy of crazy mowing. Unlock 30+unique skills such as Poison Mist, Missiles, boomerangs, formations, lightning, and more, making every battle full of excitement!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/4d2575fc201d3f87cdeadf14ecfc102a.avif?t=1737707855\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/3bfc22c32ccd52a503ac1585e63a2c66.poster.avif?t=1737707855\" width=716 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/3bfc22c32ccd52a503ac1585e63a2c66.webm?t=1737707855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/3bfc22c32ccd52a503ac1585e63a2c66.mp4?t=1737707855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Dozens of talent maps, each branch casting different advanced routes, critical damage flow, movement speed evasion flow, flesh shield armor flow, or blood sucking special effects flow, all up to you to decide!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/8c71170d9d22919eb4d729227826d32e.avif?t=1737707855\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/e9db884270b4678ef9dbcd1b2e267a7d.poster.avif?t=1737707855\" width=716 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/e9db884270b4678ef9dbcd1b2e267a7d.webm?t=1737707855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/e9db884270b4678ef9dbcd1b2e267a7d.mp4?t=1737707855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Heroes of the same type can be synthesized and upgraded to have stronger abilities. Heroes of different types can be fused according to the progression map to evolve into more powerful superheroes. How to choose the evolutionary path is the key to determining the outcome of the battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/c8c3be028125ca53f5f6c1d9d81322b9.avif?t=1737707855\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/ce3cb3e34f019551abdc0db0f71a47ba.poster.avif?t=1737707855\" width=716 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/ce3cb3e34f019551abdc0db0f71a47ba.webm?t=1737707855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3413750/extras/ce3cb3e34f019551abdc0db0f71a47ba.mp4?t=1737707855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Heroes of the same type can be synthesized and upgraded to have stronger abilities. Heroes of different types can be fused according to the progression map to evolve into more powerful superheroes. How to choose the evolutionary path is the key to determining the outcome of the battle!</p>",
